title: Doctor Salad
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small hole-in-the-wall by Ostermalmstorg. Has several raw vegan salads. All other menu items (except one) are either vegan or vegetarian. A variety of smoothies (including green), kombucha, small raw vegan treats such as brownies are available. Serves breakfast.
